rComments: Great teacher with passion for subject.

Encyclopedic knowledge of...everything. Can rattle off more history and theology than can be found in most libraries. About the kindest man you'll ever meet - entirely charming. Disorganized, but utterly brilliant.
David was great, personable, helpful, and concerned, not only with the classwork, but about your vocation. Easy to talk to. Class was a little obscure from what I expected, but good none the less.
